(76, 18, 'Mac Mini ', '9000000', '1451171971_IMG_2432.jpg', '<p><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><strong>Mac mini 2012</strong><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:rgb(20, 20, 20); font-family:helvetica,arial,sans-serif\">- CPU :&nbsp;Intel Core i5-3210M 2.5GHz (Max Turbo Frequency 3.1GHz )</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:rgb(20, 20, 20); font-family:helvetica,arial,sans-serif\">- Ram :4GB DDR3 1600MHz</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:rgb(20, 20, 20); font-family:helvetica,arial,sans-serif\">- HDD :&nbsp;128g SSD</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:rgb(20, 20, 20); font-family:helvetica,arial,sans-serif\">- VGA Intel HD Graphics 4000</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:rgb(20, 20, 20); font-family:helvetica,arial,sans-serif\">- Wifi chuẩn N</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:rgb(20, 20, 20); font-family:helvetica,arial,sans-serif\">- K&iacute;ch cỡ: 19.7 x 19.7 x 3.6 cm (m&aacute;y cực kỳ nhỏ gọn)</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:rgb(20, 20, 20); font-family:helvetica,arial,sans-serif\">- Trọng lượng chỉ 1.22 kg</span></span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<div><img alt=\"Mac Mini\" src=\"http://www.laptop2nd.vn/upload/images/IMG_2432%20(Medium).jpg\" /><img alt=\"Mac Mini\" src=\"http://www.laptop2nd.vn/upload/images/IMG_2434%20(Medium).jpg\" /><img alt=\"Mac Mini\" src=\"http://www.laptop2nd.vn/upload/images/IMG_2438%20(Medium).jpg\" /><img alt=\"Mac Mini\" src=\"http://www.laptop2nd.vn/upload/images/IMG_2444%20(Medium).jpg\" /><img alt=\"Mac Mini\" src=\"http://www.laptop2nd.vn/upload/images/IMG_2451%20(Medium).jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"section-content\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; width: 980px; margin-top: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"section-copy\" style=\"width: 750px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;\">\r\n<h1>Mac mini</h1>\r\n\r\n<h2>It&rsquo;s mini in a massive way.</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"intro\" style=\"font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.3542;\">\r\n<p>Starting at just $499.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mac&nbsp;mini is an affordable powerhouse that packs the entire Mac experience into a 7.7-inch-square frame. Just connect your own display, keyboard, and mouse, and you&rsquo;re ready to make big things happen.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"section-content\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; width: 980px; margin-top: 75px;\">\r\n<div class=\"section-copy\" style=\"width: 750px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\r\n<h2>Just big enough to ﬁt everything you want in&nbsp;a&nbsp;desktop.</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Mac&nbsp;mini makes everyday tasks a breeze with fourth-generation Intel Core processors, a flash storage option that&rsquo;s up to 50 percent faster, and wireless performance up to three times quicker than its predecessor. With Intel Iris Graphics or Intel HD Graphics 5000, it also delivers graphics performance up to 90 percent faster than the previous generation. And with great connectivity features like Thunderbolt 2 and support for HDTV, Mac&nbsp;mini makes the perfect centerpiece to any&nbsp;setup.<a class=\"more\" href=\"http://www.apple.com/mac-mini/features\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 204); text-decoration: none; white-space: nowrap;\">Learn&nbsp;more</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"section-content\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; width: 980px; margin-top: 75px;\">\r\n<div class=\"section-copy\" style=\"width: 750px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\r\n<h2>Powerfully petite.</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Carved from a solid block of aluminum, Mac&nbsp;mini has a seamless, unique look that is unmistakably Mac. At less than an inch and a half tall and under three pounds, it keeps a low profile without sacrificing functionality. And it&rsquo;s still the world&rsquo;s most energy-efficient desktop computer &mdash; it doesn&rsquo;t just meet ENERGY STAR requirements, it exceeds them up to seven times over. With a computer this compact, the only question is what to do with all that free desk&nbsp;space.&nbsp;<a class=\"more\" href=\"http://www.apple.com/mac-mini/design\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 204); text-decoration: none; white-space: nowrap;\">Learn&nbsp;more</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"section-content\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; width: 980px; margin-top: 75px;\">\r\n<div class=\"section-copy\" style=\"width: 750px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\r\n<h2>OS X El Capitan. There&rsquo;s more to love with every click.</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>OS X El Capitan brings lots of useful enhancements to your Mac. New ways to manage multiple windows and spaces. An even more powerful Spotlight for searching your Mac and beyond. Refinements to essential apps like Photos, Safari, Mail, and Maps. An all-new Notes app for gathering your thoughts and all of your content. And faster performance for nearly everything you do on your Mac &mdash; from playing games to launching apps to accessing mail.&nbsp;<a class=\"more\" href=\"http://www.apple.com/mac-mini/osx\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 204); text-decoration: none; white-space: nowrap;\">Learn&nbsp;more about OS X</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"section-content\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; width: 980px; margin-top: 75px;\">\r\n<div class=\"section-copy\" style=\"width: 750px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\r\n<h2>Great built-in apps for work&nbsp;and&nbsp;play.</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Every new Mac comes with Photos, iMovie, GarageBand, Pages, Numbers, and Keynote. So you can be creative and productive right from the start. You also get great apps for email, surfing the web, sending texts, and making FaceTime calls &mdash; there&rsquo;s even an app for finding new apps.&nbsp;<a class=\"more\" href=\"http://www.apple.com/mac-mini/built-in-apps\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 204); text-decoration: none; white-space: nowrap;\">Learn&nbsp;more</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', 1),
