 tập chơi</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><iframe frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Gfi5GbwEef8\" width=\"560\"></iframe></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><iframe frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/5Xp1J6qVFOk\" width=\"560\"></iframe></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"jjrc h37\" src=\"http://www.laptop2nd.vn/upload/images/JJRC%20H37%20Pink.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><img alt=\"jjrch37\" src=\"http://www.laptop2nd.vn/upload/images/JJRC%20H37%20Pink2.jpg\" style=\"height:918px; width:922px\" /><img alt=\"jjrch37\" src=\"http://www.laptop2nd.vn/upload/images/JJRC%20H37%20Pink8.jpg\" style=\"height:762px; width:788px\" /><img alt=\"jjrch37\" src=\"http://www.laptop2nd.vn/upload/images/JJRC%20H37%20Pink5.jpg\" style=\"height:672px; width:790px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><img alt=\"jjrch37\" src=\"http://www.laptop2nd.vn/upload/images/JJRC%20H37%20Pink7.jpg\" style=\"height:1194px; width:788px\" /><img alt=\"jjrch37\" src=\"http://www.laptop2nd.vn/upload/images/JJRC%20H37%20Pink6.jpg\" style=\"height:1162px; width:794px\" /><img alt=\"jjrch37\" src=\"http://www.laptop2nd.vn/upload/images/JJRC%20H37%20Pink3.jpg\" style=\"height:1028px; width:806px\" /><img alt=\"jjrch37\" src=\"http://www.laptop2nd.vn/upload/images/JJRC%20H37%20Pink4.jpg\" style=\"height:1108px; width:798px\" /></p>\r\n', 1);
